units metal

atom_style atomic
read_data data/water.data

neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify one 5000

timestep 0.016

thermo 1
thermo_style custom step temp ke

velocity all create 300.0 87287 mom yes rot yes dist gaussian
fix flashmd all metatomic flashmd-16.pt types 8 1 device cpu
fix thermostat all langevin 300.0 300.0 0.1 928733 zero yes

dump trajectory all custom 1 flashmd.lammpstrj id type element x y z
dump_modify trajectory sort id element O H

run 8
